Date: Thu, 26 Jun 2026 00:15:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 17/17] Harden NLB crypto and envelope auth

Fail hard on opaque decrypt errors, require hs-key for envelope HMAC,
reject TLS 1.3 portal sessions for blob decrypt, fix GnuTLS AES-192,
tighten packet type validation, and add a real HMAC-SHA1 vector test.
